Pre-Game Insights: Botswana and Cape Verde return to action in the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations qualifiers with a crucial match at Francistown Stadium.
Botswana secured a hard-fought 2-0 victory over Cape Verde in their previous encounter in Praia, aiming to do the double over the visitors.
Cape Verde, despite over 75% ball possession and numerous shots, failed to secure a win in their previous match.
